channel.title: Ranks?
channel.description:
I have been looking over some of the Moparscape Vet's, and community member's...
So far I have this:
Community member: 50rep on moparisthebest.com
Moparscape vet: No idea? I see people get it with mod, but I also see people getting it just because they post on mitb more than Mopar? Well since its MoparScape Vet, it should be like being on moparscape longer than most people, etc... Not just some silly title to go to mitbers..
Anyways... Discuss?
Also: Are they still even doing IRC legend?
